  "e333b394-fed1-4b11-8a06-ae42b0ad8b9a"],
 ", not a dense state. The two-pictures section earlier proved that the \
stabilizer and Schr\[ODoubleDot]dinger paths land on the same state; here is \
the same check at random, on a 30-gate Clifford circuit. First build the \
stream (suppressed, 30 gate specs):"
}], "Text",ExpressionUUID->"07078d55-4ae3-4c2a-a8f9-39e15e9013f3"],

